{
  "texts": [
    "The network visualization of the documents as illustrated in Fig. 5 details the interconnections between the documents through 5 clusters.",
    "To perform this visualisation, full counting was opted with the unit of analysis as Bibliometric coupling with documents.",
    "In order to narrow down the influential works, the minimum number of citations per document was set to 20.",
    "Of the 606 documents, only 40 met the threshold.",
    "Among the filtered 40 documents, only 21 items in the network had the largest set of connected items.The most influential authors of AI in language learning are listed in Table 9."
  ]
}